      "comment": "MISS JAZZ (3) comes off a fast 29.56 placing at Sandown over 515m. Hard to top on the time from last start. RADAR O'REILLY (2) took the sit on the lead but levelled up to score (30.23) at this track in Grade 6 over 525m. Deserves serious consideration again. SCOTT GREYSCALE (1) showed good speed off a low draw and there throughout but run over late when 7th over 525m at this track in a Grade 5. Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including two wins, from four starts. Warrants plenty of respect. FILL MY POCKETS (8) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
